pullRequest.body:
Add a formalization of IMO 2024 problem 3.

---

Feel free to golf; this is currently even longer than the problem 5 formalization. I suggest applying local improvements to this formalization directly to the branch, while anything that depends on new lemmas in mathlib proper might best have those lemmas PRed separately first.
